Bandejao is a project that eases the the visualization of the menu of several university's cafeterias.

<b>Features</b>:
★ Completely free and without annoying ads.
★ Don't waste your precious mobile data visiting the university website.
★ You're notified in the moment that we notice a modification in the website that has the menu.
★ Offline. Download the menu when you have Internet and then view it whenever you want.

This app shows all the available universities of this project.

If you want more about to know more about this project or if your university is not included yet, visit https://bandejao.gjhenrique.com
